data.description: Stunning and well cared for custom built home, in Broken Arrow's Whiskey Ridge! This one-of-a-kind design features a mix of traditional and transitional styles so you can enjoy the best of both worlds! There's plenty of space for everyone to spread out with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, plus and office and game room. Open and split floorplan features gourmet kitchen with quartz counters, commercial grade appliances, large walk-in pantry and pot filler open to beautiful living room boasting soaring ceilings with wood beams, cozy stone fireplace, and wall of windows overlooking backyard allowing for plenty of natural light. Primary suite, office with wood beams, and one bedroom with private bath down, and 2 bedrooms plus game room with bonus area for kids reading/play/study area up. Primary bath has his/hers sinks, soaker tub, and beautiful seamless walk-in shower w/ bench. Primary closet is oversized and opens up to laundry and mud room/drop zone. Enjoy your morning cup of coffee or relax in the evenings on the spacious A-frame back patio with partial greenbelt/pond view. Spray-foam insulation, 16 SEER AC, 95% efficient furnace. Short distance to community pool and just minutes from creek turnpike for easy access to any part of the city. Assumable VA loan at 2.875% for qualifying VA buyers!!!
